{"tid":114501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國河口，已成超級病菌繁殖場","createTime":"2017-02-09T22:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T03:02:00.000Z","uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ba99cabf1c3f839071ca51a42a0175351220c7d","tid":114501,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T22:17:04.000Z","msg":"cpu 媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n據估計，到 2050 年，每年將有 1,000 萬人死於感染耐藥性病菌，取代癌症成為人類頭號殺手。問題嚴重，不少科學家反覆調查錯在何處，從執業醫生的開藥習慣，到病人食抗生素半途而廢留下禍端，乃至農場為食用禽畜濫用抗生素。最新研究指，連接內陸與海洋的河口，也是抗藥基因的集散地，至少在中國如是。<br />\n<br />\n自然期刊日前刊登論文，研究人員在中國走遍 4,000 公里海岸線，化驗所有河口的污水，發現全部樣本均帶有抗藥基因，甚至是殘留抗生素。原來是居民處理排污失當，將帶有具抗生素耐藥性基因的排泄物直接流入河道，令河口成為超級病菌的搖籃，日後大部分河鮮都可能帶有超級耐藥抗體。<br />\n<br />\n研究指由於抗藥細菌散播廣泛，人類的腸道細菌以及微生物組多少帶有抗藥性基因。本來這些細菌對人體無害，而且抗藥基因為數不多，無傷大雅，但當這些細菌隨人類排泄物流入受污染河道及水道，就能釀成大禍。澳洲分子進化學教授 Michael Gillings 和其他研究人員的研究揭露，這些抗體基因儼然是中國各個河口的主要污染物，部分河口甚至每克泥沙就有 1 億個抗藥基因。河口是與海水接壤之地，是內陸污水及海洋之間的自然過濾點，滯留四方而來的污染物，變成抗藥基因累積的重災區。<br />\n<br />\n更嚴重者，除了污水中的抗藥基因，河口更累積大量經人類或動物服用後排出的抗生素殘留物，難以分解，與消毒劑、重金屬和其他市區河道污染物合流，為自然生態系統中的細菌提供源源不絕的免疫訓練，練就多種抗藥抗重金屬抗消毒劑的基因，大大增加細菌生存優勢。研究人員指，在這些河口出現的病菌，部分擁有前所未見的抗藥基因組合。倘若抗藥基因被從未在人類或動物之間造成健康影響的病菌吸收，將造就新的超級病菌。<br />\n<br />\n不少河鮮來自這些河口，如蝦蟹蠔魚，牠們以河床沉積物為食，人類又以牠們為食，成為將新超級病菌進口人類社會的直接渠道。<br />\n<br />\nGillings 指，此次研究在家禽業經常大量使用抗生素的中國進行，反映的河口實況可能較為極端，但相信問題在其他地方同樣出現。看來要減少超級病毒進化機會，除了慎用抗生素外，如何有效移除抗生素及其他污染物的污水處理也是一重要命題。"},{"pid":"f2730fc976b5876a02f3253da44033a6e51fe797","tid":114501,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:00:52.000Z","msg":"借問聲珠江河口響邊"},{"pid":"7090b6e4e102827cb84762037ae81fcf8d99eeb6","tid":114501,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借問聲珠江河口響邊</blockquote><br />\n香港左上角"},{"pid":"f0c14282977bfdd915dbf03343f180b77e4916a3","tid":114501,"uid":65619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>借問聲珠江河口響邊</blockquote><br />\n香港左上角</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d4876094345acd82ff81c2c82290dc8c701ae7","tid":114501,"uid":45551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>借問聲珠江河口響邊</blockquote><br />\n香港左上角</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db724d61181f32c4c5be0ec1f5695e7d5973275","tid":114501,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:40:24.000Z","msg":"犀利"},{"pid":"75d4d1d30a1a5c1bd4893826f712b06ebf19575f","tid":114501,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>借問聲珠江河口響邊</blockquote><br />\n香港左上角</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屯門對出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15da26c5e4ed0df6478f2f2f322d681966c0eb31","tid":114501,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:50:33.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"a27b5781f806f140af8f20713d9525c05a576a36","tid":114501,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:51:51.000Z","msg":"河口華"},{"pid":"066723e136e3c64130e4aad2d83ab1bae4cce3dc","tid":114501,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T01:03:35.000Z","msg":"當初美國唔應該為咗抗蘇俄對支那隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n依家支那坐大喺度也文也武輸出腐敗<br />\n核電廠四圍都係 (支共出品安全性大家心照)<br />\n毒霧酸霧核霧(高含鈾量煤唔提煉反而攞去燒)日日都有<br />\n連啲人同環境都變成超級細菌嘅搖籃<br />\n第時冚球剷真係多得支那唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104a4852101e2a3b86b43b2b18c1cdfcacc952d0","tid":114501,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T01:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>河口華</blockquote><br />\n做咩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8888c014d32e8021c5b11bc68d5bba5430f0d966","tid":114501,"uid":21277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"有冇Source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611ba16de6c9570364f306401dff296c41e72278","tid":114501,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇Source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsearch過係2013已經有相關報導, 近期CUP又攞出嚟報 (好似係)<br />\n英文反而搵到今年一月尾STAT News出咗篇文講有研究發現支那醫院多咗帶超級病菌基因嘅細菌 (篇研究啱啱喺The Lancet發表咗)<br />\n隻基因叫mcr-1, 唔單止大部分抗生素, 就連被視為最後防線嘅colistin都頂到<br />\n依家發現研究調查嘅兩間支那醫院(其中一間喺廣東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)有1%大腸桿菌同肺炎桿菌有mcr-1基因<br />\n<br />\ncolistin副作用太大喺外國唔經常用, 用得多數係因為其他抗生素都冇效, 所以本來唔應該有好多細菌產生對抗到呢隻藥嘅基因, 醫院亦都當佢係最後防線<br />\n偏偏支那大量用喺豬場刺激豬隻生長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba77bc21dcc8ac71bc3c4ac92867a083251f98dd","tid":114501,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"廢中廢老：大菌食細菌，細菌當補品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95169e50d4cb0f86329a5094318983b6be005fde","tid":114501,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇Source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsearch過係2013已經有相關報導, 近期CUP又攞出嚟報 (好似係)<br />\n英文反而搵到今年一月尾STAT News出咗篇文講有研究發現支那醫院多咗帶超級病菌基因嘅細菌 (篇研究啱啱喺The Lancet發表咗)<br />\n隻基因叫mcr-1, 唔單止大部分抗生素, 就連被視為最後防線嘅colistin都頂到<br />\n依家發現研究調查嘅兩間支那醫院(其中一間喺廣東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)有1%大腸桿菌同肺炎桿菌有mcr-1基因<br />\n<br />\ncolistin副作用太大喺外國唔經常用, 用得多數係因為其他抗生素都冇效, 所以本來唔應該有好多細菌產生對抗到呢隻藥嘅基因, 醫院亦都當佢係最後防線<br />\n偏偏支那大量用喺豬場刺激豬隻生長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那永遠冇好帶挈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要累到陷球隡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}